snippet.title: Official Trailer - Minecraft Xbox 360 Edition
snippet.description:
Watch the Setup video here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ih-8LZD3ekY
Watch the Multiplayer Overview here: http://youtu.be/iar8k4gmslY
Watch the New Minecraft Series: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2BC6E424F1D3B451&feature=view_all

Welcome to Minecraft Xbox 360 Edition, here's a taste of multiplayer action coming to Xbox Live Arcade on May 9th.
Make sure to use a HD television when playing with friends on split screen.

►Check out Hat Films channel here: http://www.youtube.com/user/HaatFilms?feature=mhee

►Featured Music:

♫ Check out C418's Original "Sweden" here: 
http://c418.bandcamp.com/

♫ Check out Crimson & Crisis' Remix here: 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zk-DaZ_wB4A&list=PL8FF106DAE9944209&index=1&feature=plcp
